{"tid":1534393,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好以為好好笑，合理地懷疑警犬有濫用精神科藥物","createTime":"2019-09-03T03:45:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-03T16:46:04.000Z","uid":28770,"like":45,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"e358577dc194a8af6105a5291a453de21a7d6b17","tid":1534393,"uid":28770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:45:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/rMwrGY6.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrMwrGY6.gif&h=7e712ab3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當大家笑緊呢條片嗰時<br />\n<br />\n有無諗過點解一個人會有呢種接近失控嘅反應？<br />\n<br />\n飲red bull飲得太多？純粹因為唔夠瞓？<br />\n<br />\n如果沿住服用過量精神科藥物嘅角度去諗⋯⋯<br />\n<br />\n佢哋服藥會係個人嘅行為定係上頭嘅命令？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我知我知⋯⋯到呢刻以上嘅嘢都未能fact check<br />\n只係一個推論⋯⋯但只少沿住呢個方向諗過<br />\n<br />\n下次再出現類似嘅情況更加唔可以掉以輕心。"},{"pid":"0693a28f60ba4f700c059cda051df6022c3da907","tid":1534393,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:45:23.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">9月8！到時見！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8e8f8aac87310c334594abb3d9d880781294bc93","tid":1534393,"uid":266362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-03T03:45:34.000Z","msg":"跪求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">想大個仔獨立必睇</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">召喚攬炒巴及歷